This extension adds Spotify and Grooveshark links to the songs playing in 8tracks
An Unofficial 8tracks Extension

8tracksharkify adds Grooveshark and Spotify links to the songs played in 8tracks. 

You often come across songs you really love. You want to save them to listen again. Mostly you open Spotify or Grooveshark, copy the name and search it. 

Now it is just one click with little buttons appearing next to the track.

